        <p><span>Winter sports in Himachal Pradesh make it a popular tourist destination both during summer and winter season. If trekking is a popular summer adventure sport, then skiing and ice skating are top winter adventure sports. You can enjoy ice skating in Himachal Pradesh from mid December to February. Indian Holiday gives you the details Ice skating sites in Himachal Pradesh Ice skating can only be done on a flat surface with a thick layer of ice.</span></p></td>
